quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  78,31,"S tidep, i wid ipêezziben, amkan n laman"
  78,32,"tifeôôanin, iqwiôen"
  78,33,tizzyiwin ifazen
  78,34,lkisan ifalen
  78,35,Ur din sellen yir awal ne$ tikerkas
  78,36,"D arraz s$uô Mass ik, d tikci klalen"
  78,37,"Mass n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen; Aênin, ur zmiren a ten Ioo a d mmeslayen"
  78,38,"Asmi ara beddent lmalayek akked ôôuê, d idurra, siwa win Iooa Uênin ara d immeslayen; a d yini awal uûwib"
  78,39,"D wagi ay d ass n tidep; win ib$an, idda d ubrid n tu$alin ar Mass is"
  78,40,"Ih, Nâaggen awen: aâaqeb d ayen iqeôben. Ass ideg ara iéeô umdan, acu xedmen ifassen is, ad yini ujehli: \"a ssexv iw, a lemmer lli$ d akal"